welcome_message_body: Welcome to Lakeville, where the charm of our picturesque lakes and vibrant community awaits you. Known for its beautiful scenery and friendly locals, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, primarily serving low-cost carriers and regional flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport, but may require a brief registration process.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Downtown Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
